#

Truffle Parmesan Fettuccine with Grilled Asparagus and Lemon Zest

$18.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Tags:

PastaGourmetVegetarian

Description

Indulge in creamy fettuccine infused with truffle oil, topped with savory Parmesan and complemented by vibrant grilled asparagus and a hint of citrus zest.

Ingredients

  • Fettuccine: 8 oz
  • Truffle oil: 2 tbsp
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Lemon zest: 1 tsp
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
